commit.message:
toplev.c: Include alloc-pool.h.

2004-01-30  Andrew Pinski <pinskia@physics.uc.edu>

        * toplev.c: Include alloc-pool.h.
        * Makefile.in (toplev.c): Update dependencies.

From-SVN: r76976
